Whatever helps you forget,
get out of here, go on.

1033
00:57:23,458 --> 00:57:24,458
[door closes]

1034
00:57:29,958 --> 00:57:30,958
Damn it.

1035
00:57:38,583 --> 00:57:39,583
[breathing heavily]

1036
00:57:46,041 --> 00:57:47,041
Is she dead?

1037
