Oh, Jeff, we may wanna reconsider
the community snack bowl, given, uh…

1230
01:10:16,208 --> 01:10:17,208
Shit-finger.

1231
01:10:17,250 --> 01:10:19,916
Yeah. Have a wonderful evening.

1232
01:10:20,916 --> 01:10:22,166
- And you.
- And you.

1233
01:11:02,916 --> 01:11:03,916
[whispering] Bingo.

